formulaVisited 
 
Class Environment 
 
java.lang.Object
    formulaVisited.Environment 
 
    public class  Environment   extends java.lang.Object    
An environment in which to evaluate a formula.
  The environment may contain definitions of logical variables (true or false).
  

  
   



  
     
